sampled from standard MD simulation of Na4Zr2(SiO4)3 at 500 K. Bottom: The progress of the tagged Na+ ion in the super-cell during the MTD
simulation of Na4Zr2(SiO4)3 at 500 K highlighted for the first 100 ns in red, and that of the next 100–200 ns in olive green.

